metadata.name: Wolf#1
metadata.description: A specially curated collection of 1,700 Wolf NFTs. The Wolf Pack implements a lifetime royalty for all minters and a reflection tax to all current holders. We are building an NFT fighting game with utility, where the community will be able to compete in tournaments and win rare NFTs. A 10 Den utility token is also in the works that will be used inside the game and will allow token holders to earn yield.
